desc_short	-----								Divide By Sheep is a mind-bending math puzzler about friendship and slicing sheep in half with lasers. The Grim Reaper flooded the world, and it's up to you to save critters stranded on islands. Insane math skills required.							
developer									Victor Solodilov					,			Denis Novikov								
